metadata.name: Gallery ENTITIES META
metadata.description:
GmGn Fam I am glad to present to you my fantasy for the ENTITIES META collection, which I was inspired by by chance seeing Vasily Popov's interview on YouTube. I was inspired by the fact that a man has achieved success in his creative path, and was the first to launch into space a physical copy of the NFT with the image of an astronaut from his ENTITIES META collection. Below I will present all links to the author of this collection, as well as links to my collections.
